    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;Since the publication of the RFCs specifying Version 1.0 of the Internet Open Trading Protocol (IOTP), some errors have been noted.  This informational document lists these errors and provides corrections for them.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
